name: Alex Bartsch X ManzanoArte - Tear Down

metadata.name: Tear Down #1
metadata.description:
Luis "Enano" Bogado, the co-founder of ManzanoArte, pulls up the floor after the show in El Pozo. Along with Zoribel Garcia, Enano opened up their house in Carayaca and turned it into a Social Circus in order to teach the local kids life changing skills. They also run a yearly festival to showcase the kids' talents but also to bring international performers for workshops and to participate in the festival.

Tear Down is a collection of images shot during the tear down of the ManzanoArte Festival show in the community of El Pozo in the state of Vargas in Venezuela. All proceeds to go to the ManzanoArte Foundation.
